tweet: Day one in the books. I could not be more excited to serve the residents of our state.  Thank you to @GovMurphy for the confidence you have placed in me.   As promised, we got right to work. Looking forward to tomorrow.

name: Matt Platkin
tweet: Andrew Bruck was a friend long before he became a colleague. He is a true public servant to whom every New Jerseyan owes a debt of gratitude — and I know his impact is only just beginning. I thank him for his exemplary service and wish him and his beautiful family my very best.

name: Matt Platkin
tweet: I am grateful, from the bottom of my heart, to @GovMurphy for the trust he has placed in me. And thank you to my good friend @NewJerseyOAG Andrew Bruck for his exemplary service to the state. I will work tirelessly to protect the 9m residents who call this great state home.
